headline: Wall Street coasts toward the end of another winning month
summary: U.S. stocks are coasting toward the finish of Wall Street’s latest winning month on Tuesday.  The S&P 500 slipped 0.2% in early trading, but the main measure of the U.S. stock market’s health remains on track for a fifth straight winning month after setting a record last week.
